      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "INCA TRAIL (1) continues to race consistently, backing up a recent win with a close second at Rockhampton last start. He tends to hold his form once fit and looks well placed to go one better here. DIVAKARA (2) is unbeaten on this surface and had little luck on turf last time when caught wide throughout. The booking of Bailey Wheeler is a positive and he shapes as one of the main dangers. VREDEFORT (6) had excuses here 16 days ago after covering ground early before struggling to finish off. With the field reduced by scratchings, he gets his chance to bounce back into the money. ROARING SUCCESS (9) enjoys racing at this track and is generally around the mark, making him a must for exotics. ORMOND ROAD (8) also has claims in a small field.",
